<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
    <title>Visualizations - MeX AI Companion Documentation</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/highlight.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1>Interactive Visualizations</h1>
        <p class="lead">Explore the MeX AI Companion architecture, components, and relationships through these interactive visualizations.</p>

        <div class="visualization-container mt-5">
            <h2 class="visualization-title">Duality Model Visualization</h2>
            <p class="visualization-description">This visualization illustrates the core Duality Model architecture of the MeX AI Companion, showing the Mirror Component, Bridge Component, and Synthesis Layer with their respective subcomponents.</p>
            <div id="duality-model-visualization" style="width: 100%; height: 500px;"></div>
            <div id="component-info-panel" class="component-info-panel mt-3"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="visualization-container mt-5">
            <h2 class="visualization-title">Component Relationship Diagram</h2>
            <p class="visualization-description">This force-directed graph shows how different components of the MeX AI Companion system interact with each other. Drag nodes to explore relationships.</p>
            <div id="component-relationship-diagram" style="width: 100%; height: 600px;"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="visualization-container mt-5">
            <h2 class="visualization-title">Ethical Framework Visualization</h2>
            <p class="visualization-description">This treemap visualization represents the ethical framework that guides the MeX AI Companion, including core principles, implementation mechanisms, and ethical guardrails.</p>
            <div id="ethical-framework-visualization" style="width: 100%; height: 500px;"></div>
            <div id="ethics-info-panel" class="ethics-info-panel mt-3"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="visualization-container mt-5">
            <h2 class="visualization-title">User Flow Diagram</h2>
            <p class="visualization-description">This diagram illustrates typical user flows and interactions with the MeX AI Companion, from onboarding through various interfaces and rituals.</p>
            <div id="user-flow-diagram" style="width: 100%; height: 600px;"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/d3.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/visualizations.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
